                    <p class="text-gray-400">OSINT → Subdomain Discovery → Port Scan → Live Probing → Crawling → Historical Mining → Vulnerability Scan</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🎯</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-purple-400">Autonomous Bug Bounty Mode</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400">Single-mode pipeline focused on bug bounty recon and reporting with safe defaults.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🛡️</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-pink-400">Compliance Mapping</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400">Every vulnerability tagged with SOC2, ISO-27001, and GDPR compliance violations. Perfect for enterprise audits.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🔍</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-yellow-400">5 OSINT Modules</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400">Certificate transparency, GitHub secret hunting, cloud bucket enumeration, DNS analysis, technology fingerprinting.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="feature-card">
